high_descs: Pick up the bar of soap to the left of the spray bottle.
Walk across the room to the vanity.
Get the soap wet in the sink on the left.
Take the wet soap back to the toilet.
Stand the wet bar of soap on its end on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: turn left to face the toilet
grab the bar of soap off of the top of the toilet to the left of the left candle
turn around and walk past the toilet a bit, then take a left and walk to the left side sink
place the soap in the sink and turn the water on to rinse it off
return back to the toilet to your left
place the soap back on top of the toilet but to the right this time
anns.task_desc: place a rinsed off bar of soap on top of the toilet

high_descs: Move to the left side of the toilet.
Pick the soap up from the back of the toilet.
Turn around and approach the sink?
Put the soap in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water and take the soap out of the sink.
Move to the left and stand facing the right side of the toilet.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put clean soap on the back of the toilet.
